05:38.440 --> 05:39.280
Komandan,

05:39.600 --> 05:40.960
Tuan yang adil,

05:41.400 --> 05:43.520
Anda harus membela saya.

05:43.920 --> 05:45.640
Bela saya.

05:46.120 --> 05:47.080
Komandan Resimen Liu.

05:47.080 --> 05:47.800
Hadir.

05:48.320 --> 05:49.560
Pria yang direkrut paksa seperti ini,

05:49.560 --> 05:51.090
