10:16.440 --> 10:17.570
Kembali ke barisan!

10:28.560 --> 10:30.080
Titik jatuhnya peluru tersebar.

10:30.080 --> 10:31.520
Meriam kapal kaliber besar.

10:31.520 --> 10:32.880
